<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4 font-semibold">
      <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Gli avverbi danno una sfumatura di significato particolare a un verbo, a un aggettivo o a un altro avverbio. Possono essere:
    </p>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di modo</strong> (come?) → bene, male, volentieri… e gli avverbi che si formano unendo il suffisso <strong>-mente</strong> a un aggettivo (lentamente...)</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di quantità</strong> (quanto?) → molto, poco, troppo, più, meno, assai, abbastanza…</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di luogo</strong> (dove?) → qui, lì, qua, là, giù, lassù, dentro, davanti, sopra…</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di tempo</strong> (quando?) → ora, adesso, oggi, ieri, domani, già, spesso, mai, poi, sempre, presto, tardi…</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di affermazione</strong> → sì, certo, sicuramente, appunto, davvero...</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di negazione</strong> → no, non, neppure, mica…</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di dubbio</strong> → forse, probabilmente, eventualmente, magari, circa…</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="false">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Sottolinea gli avverbi<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-yellow-300 rounded ml-1"></span>
    </h2>

    <!-- Color Selector (hidden for mono-color) -->
    <div class="hidden">
      <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-yellow-300" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="yellow"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Mi ha salutato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">affettuosamente</span>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> I ladri scapparono <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">assai</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">lontano</span>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Sono venuto <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">appunto</span> per questo.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Certo</span>, ti aiuto <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">volentieri</span>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Probabilmente</span> vinceremo il concorso.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Spesso</span> parli <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">troppo</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">forte</span>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Vieni <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">qua</span> con me.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Forse</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">domani</span> nevicherà anche <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">qui</span>.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Esercizi p. <%= link_to "176", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p176"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %> e <%= link_to "179", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p179"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
